{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"45646-el-teegray","title":"El Tigre","description":"¡Cuando un tigre camina en el bosque, todos los animales y las aves saben! Escuchar los sonidos diferentes de los animales ,  advierte a todos los animales cuando el tigre está aquí.","language":"Spanish","langCode":"es","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Adam Knell"],"illustrators":["Rohan Chakravarty"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"StoryWeaver Community","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/45646-el-teegray"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/495589/size3/0ffeaffc8b06617aca654bbe2fa9542b.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/495589/size6/0ffeaffc8b06617aca654bbe2fa9542b.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/48378/size6/d6762057368d196d85e6659c017ed4a3.jpg","text":"No es fácil ser un tigre. \nSí, los tigres son lindos y feroces.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/48379/size6/e7d4148f8437a720ddb0e115ddd21b64.jpg","text":"Pero los tigres son también grandes y pesados. \nEsto  hace difícil para ellos cazar comida.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/48380/size6/dd66a1cfaccef0a7b72696b9d42a65a3.jpg","text":"Un tigre come una vez, después de veinte intentos.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/48381/size6/dc1adfd806cace6969c6a3c2b446ca7b.jpg","text":"¡Cuando un tigre camina a través del bosque, \n¡COF!  ¡COF! ¡COF!\nEl  langur suena, como un viejo tosiendo!\nCOF! COF! COF!","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/48901/size6/48e24ba81e63bc56a70a994095150e2d.jpg","text":"AUUUU! JAUUUU!\n¡El ciervo ladrando suena como un perro asustado!\nAUUUU! JAUUUU!","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/48902/size6/400d34cd99255ab56c87c33b189fde25.jpg","text":"AÚ! AÚ! AÚ!\n¡El ciervo manchado suena como un pájaro pequeño!\nAÚ! AÚ! AÚ!","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/48905/size6/49c768d7866a991b3291cb47ecd2d1aa.jpg","text":"Todo el bosque sabe que él tigre está aquí.\nAJUUUN! AJUUUN!\nEl tigre no sabe dónde están todos animales.","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":7,"words":103}}